Phase 6: Reminders and Study Materials

- Email reminder cron API (/api/cron/reminders) with 4 reminder types: streak encouragement, weak area nudge, exam approaching, and general study nudge. Uses nodemailer, protected by CRON_SECRET, scheduled daily at 9am via Vercel Cron.
- Study materials API (/api/materials) with GET/POST/DELETE. Stores text content in Firestore (up to 500K chars). Supports notes, PDF text, study guides, slides.
- Study materials UI at /dashboard/materials with upload form (title, type, content textarea with char counter), materials list with delete, and empty state.
- Vercel cron schedule added to vercel.json
- All 6 dashboard cards now active and linked

